data.description: WHAT A NICE MAINTAINED HOME AT A NICE PRICE! Need a little extra room and struggling to find it, well this home may be the one.  This Tri-Level home features 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and a spacious down stairs flex/bonus space.  Master bedroom upstairs has it's own bathroom with standing shower.  There are 2 additional bedrooms upstairs and a hallway bathroom with shower/tub combo.  On the middle level, you will find your living room, dinning area, and kitchen.  Downstairs, is the flex/bonus space with 1/2 bath/laundry, closets for additional storage, and a walkout to the patio.  Keep the gazebo and outdoor shed as a gift.  Home also has additional storage off the carport. Home is well maintained and cared for with some updates over the Sellers ownership and the previous long term owner; however, it leaves enough room for any new owner to put their stamp on it.  It's priced accordingly, so what are you waiting for, grab your Agent and schedule a showing today!
